  <verse number="8" style="v" />For from you the word of the Lord has rung out, and not only in Macedonia and Achaia. Instead, to every place your faith in God has gone out. As a result, we do not need to say anything.

  <verse number="9" style="v" />For they themselves report what kind of coming we had among you. They tell how you turned to God from the idols to serve the living and true God.

  <verse number="10" style="v" />They report that you are waiting for his Son from heaven, whom he raised from the dead ones. This is Jesus, who frees us from the wrath to come.</para>
